comments: Hunter (ATL) wraps Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) that affects his ability to get to the pass.
Hollis-Jefferson (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Bembry (ATL) following the rebound.
Collins (ATL) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by Hollis-Jefferson (TOR).
McCaw (TOR) makes contact to Young's (ATL) body after the release that affects his ability to land safely.
Bembry (ATL) makes contact to Siakam's (TOR) arm that affects his ability to make the pass.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Siakam (TOR) throws the ball out of bounds.
Young (ATL) releases from McCaw (TOR) at the end of his drive and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Powell (TOR) touched the ball after it has reached its apex and is on its way down.
VanVleet (TOR) releases from Huerter (ATL) at the end of his drive and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Reddish (ATL) delivers contact to VanVleet's (TOR) body that affects his SQBR.
Collins (ATL) goes through VanVleet's (TOR) body and makes contact that causes him to go to the floor.  The contact occurs after VanVleet's shooting motion and this should be a personal foul.
Carter (ATL) makes contact with VanVleet (TOR) as he extends his backside into VanVleet's path, but the contact is marginal.
Huerter (ATL) releases from Powell (TOR) at the end of the drive and does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Carter (ATL) commits a take foul on VanVleet (TOR).
